Title: Sublime
Description: Instances of the sublime in the world

Title: limbic capitalism ◱
Description:
The bottom left quadrant of the [political compass ⛋](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/political-compass-gt_m7qw2cq4): low in wisdom and care, low in power and competitive capacity.

Not quite an ideology anyone conscious would choose to follow, but a system of persuasion and control that engenders addiction and nihilism on those it captures.

Title: techno-optimism ◰
Description:
The top right quadrant of the [political compass ⛋](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/political-compass-gt_m7qw2cq4): high in power and competitive capacity, low in wisdom and care.

It's the ideology of the [Technium](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/technium)

Plagued by [Moloch](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/moloch-vtdjdv6injm), [game theory ♛](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/game-theory-h7aouz5lohu), [Instrumental Convergence](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/instrumental-convergence). 

[e/acc, Accelerationism](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/e-acc-accelerationism) is the more aggressive form of it, [Limbic Capitalism](https://www.are.na/welf-von-horen/limbic-capitalism-ukq3evfh1om) the consumer reality it creates.
